q3r6: A period of vibrant tranquility that can bring you pleasures, new discoveries and some unexpected blessings.

q3r8: Dreams of abundant wealth, dazzling success and joyous celebration fill your life and lift you up
q4r1: Your worry and sadness are unfounded - on the contrary, success and good fortune is due to arrive.
q4r2: There are no obstacles to your freedom or happiness. Do not get pulled into passing moods that say otherwise.
q4r3: Whatever has been causing you worry will be transformed into unexpected joy and your birth into a new state.
q4r4: If you are willing to let go of your inner turmoil, you will find what you are seeking in abundance.
q4r5: If your outlook is clear and persistent, what was in decline can now be turned around and revitalized.
q4r6: Be at peace and retreat to quietness and reflection. It is not a time to make difficult choices or to seek certainty.
q4r7: By being open and generous, turbulence lifts and blessings come that bring you love and good fortune.
q4r8: Temporary melancholy and darkness. What is sought now will not be obtained now. Wait patiently.
